# Summary
This documentation details the Mailchimp integration with Amplitude, allowing users to import Mailchimp subscribe/unsubscribe events, send Amplitude cohorts to Mailchimp, and personalize messaging. The setup process involves connecting Amplitude to a specific Mailchimp audience through authorization and webhook creation.

